/// 10-byte PIPE (0x0080) START header that follows the 2 opcode bytes (host->device). If
/// flags bit1 (PIPE_FLAG_PARTIAL) is set, a 12-byte PipePartialExt is appended (22 bytes
/// total after the opcode). NOTE: the plan inventory listed this as 8 bytes, but the field
